data.description: This is a beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath house located in the heart of Azle, Texas. There are just too many upgrades to list but I will point out the tiled porches (front and back), upgraded faucets, upgraded lighting ,fireplace tiles, quartz countertops, kitchen backsplash, shiplap entry wall and many more; this is a must see!!
